c: 22
v: 18
t: "Ese ntubona ko ibiri mu birere n’ibiri ku isi, izuba, ukwezi, inyenyeri, imisozi, ibiti, ibiremwa byose bigenda ku isi ndetse na benshi mu bantubyubamira Allah? Ariko abenshi (mu bantu) bakwiye ibihano. Kandi uwo Allah yasuzuguje ntawamwubaha, kuko mu by’ukuri Allah akora ibyo ashatse"